Another axis

The more interesting realization is that these aren’t mutually exclusive.

Imagine each as a force vector instead of a destination.

A company might operate through:

* 40% hierarchy
* 20% protocol
* 20% culture
* 20% reputation

An open-source project might be:

* protocol
* reputation
* merit
* voluntary participation

A family:

* affection
* tradition
* hierarchy (for children)
* reciprocity

