Timing deserves its own axis

Your fireworks story hints at something that isn’t usually listed.

Timing.

Everyone had access to roughly the same information.

The difference wasn’t intelligence.

It wasn’t authority.

It wasn’t even courage.

It was:

acting at the right moment with the right amount of movement.

That makes timing its own coordination resource.

